      "DefaultValue": "// Attributes: vel, col, pos, idx \n\n// Very simple examples:\nfloat3 vp = pos - Offset;\nfloat d = length(vp);\nfloat f = smoothstep(A,B+1,d);\nvel-= vp/(d+0.0001);"
